<item>
            <title>[HADOOP-9791] Add a test case covering long paths for new FileUtil access check methods</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-9791</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We&apos;ve seen historically that paths longer than 260 chars can cause things not to work on Windows if not properly handled. Filing a tracking Jira to add a native io test case with long paths for new FileUtil access check methods added with &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-9413&quot; title=&quot;Introduce common utils for File#setReadable/Writable/Executable and File#canRead/Write/Execute that work cross-platform&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HADOOP-9413&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HADOOP-9413&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
